{"tid":2208941,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美次卿訪台｜共軍再派19架戰機越中線 台空軍升空驅離 防空飛彈監控","createTime":"2020-09-19T09:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T13:17:23.000Z","uid":239336,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3f5248b548eef4098eba87ad9c5f863debea7d","tid":2208941,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"美國國務院次卿克拉奇、日本前首相森喜朗今（19）日出席已故前總統李登輝告別禮拜，沒想到共軍繼昨日派出18架軍機擾台，其中12架飛越海峽中線後，今日上午共機再次出現西部空域，台空軍除全程掌握，更罕見首度以重話廣播回擊「立即迴轉脫離，一切後果自負！」台國防部今中午於發佈消息指，今天共有12架殲16機、 2架殲10機、 2架殲11機、2架轟6機及1架運8反潛機，共19架軍機擾台，還飛越海峽中線。國防部派遣空中巡邏及緊急起飛等兵力應對，進行廣播驅離及防空飛彈追監。<br />\n<br />\n根據台灣《自由時報》報道，航空軌跡及廣播紀錄，早上7點起共軍持續多方向多批次多空層侵擾台海，台空軍持續對西北空域、西部空域，西南空域入侵空域之共機進行廣播驅離程序，其中，上午9點20分左右，空軍對西部空域高度7,000米共機廣播內容與過去不同，內容為<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「中華民國空軍廣播，位於台灣西部空域高度7,000米的中共軍機注意！你已接近我領空，影響我飛行安全，立即迴轉脫離，一切後果自負！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/4PAWJPB2BZCXJENERVWBK5RAGE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1jRn8qYwoyJhyhNfPfMOSvjR-oNon4kTL8WzwYeB-BNpDvMoxqrVqgblo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2F4PAWJPB2BZCXJENERVWBK5RAGE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1jRn8qYwoyJhyhNfPfMOSvjR-oNon4kTL8WzwYeB-BNpDvMoxqrVqgblo&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCuaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=ced3a33b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2F4PAWJPB2BZCXJENERVWBK5RAGE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1jRn8qYwoyJhyhNfPfMOSvjR-oNon4kTL8WzwYeB-BNpDvMoxqrVqgblo&h=85749c76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/4PAWJPB2BZCXJENERVWBK5RAGE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk